# 1. Architecture nima?

Architecture — tizimning yuqori darajadagi tuzilishi.

Masalan uy qurishda:

```txt
Poydevor
↓
Qavatlar
↓
Xonalar
↓
Elektr tizimi
↓
Suv tizimi
```

Dasturda:

```txt
Frontend
↓
Backend
↓
Database
↓
Infrastructure
```

Architecture tizim qismlarini qanday tashkil qilishni belgilaydi.

---

# Nega Architecture kerak?

Architecture bo'lmasa:

* Kod chalkashib ketadi
* O'zgartirish qiyinlashadi
* Test yozish qiyin bo'ladi
* Performance pasayadi
* Katta jamoa ishlay olmaydi

Architecture maqsadi:

```txt
Maintainability
Scalability
Testability
Reusability
Flexibility
```

---

# 2. Architecture Pattern nima?

Architecture Pattern — tizimni qurish uchun oldindan sinovdan o'tgan yechim.

Masalan:

```txt
MVC
MVVM
Clean Architecture
Microservices
```

Bularning har biri muayyan muammoni hal qiladi.

---

# 3. MVC (Model View Controller)

Eng mashhur patternlardan biri.

1979-yilda yaratilgan.

---

## Strukturasi

```txt
User
 ↓
Controller
 ↓
Model
 ↓
Database

Controller
 ↓
View
 ↓
User
```

---

## Model

Business logic va data bilan ishlaydi.

Masalan:

```txt
User
Product
Order
Invoice
```

Model:

```js
class User {
  id
  name
  email
}
```

---

## View

Foydalanuvchi ko'radigan UI.

Masalan:

```txt
Login Page
Dashboard
Profile
```

---

## Controller

View va Model o'rtasidagi vositachi.

Misol:

```txt
Login Button
 ↓
Controller
 ↓
User Service
 ↓
Database
```

---

## Request Lifecycle

```txt
User
 ↓
Controller
 ↓
Model
 ↓
Database
 ↓
Controller
 ↓
View
 ↓
User
```

---

## MVC Afzalliklari

### Separation of Concerns

Har qism alohida javobgar.

### Test qilish oson

Controller va Model alohida test qilinadi.

### Katta tizimlar uchun qulay

---

## MVC Kamchiliklari

### Controller semirib ketadi

Katta loyihalarda:

```txt
UserController
= 5000 qator kod
```

bo'lib qoladi.

---

## MVC ishlatiladigan frameworklar

* Laravel
* ASP.NET MVC
* Spring MVC
* Ruby on Rails

---

# 4. MVT (Model View Template)

Asosan Django ishlatadi.

---

## Strukturasi

```txt
User
 ↓
View
 ↓
Model
 ↓
Database

View
 ↓
Template
 ↓
User
```

---

## MVC bilan farqi

MVC:

```txt
Controller
↓
View
```

MVT:

```txt
View
↓
Template
```

Djangoda Controller vazifasini View bajaradi.

---

## Model

Database bilan ishlaydi.

```python
class User(models.Model):
    name = models.CharField()
```

---

## View

Requestlarni qabul qiladi.

```python
def users(request):
    users = User.objects.all()
```

---

## Template

UI yaratadi.

```html
{{ user.name }}
```

---

## MVT Afzalliklari

* Django bilan juda qulay
* CRUD tez yoziladi
* Admin panel tayyor

---

## MVT Kamchiliklari

* Business Logic View ichida aralashib ketishi mumkin

---

# 5. MVP (Model View Presenter)

Android va Desktop dasturlarda ko'p ishlatilgan.

---

## Strukturasi

```txt
View
 ↕
Presenter
 ↕
Model
```

---

## View

Faqat UI.

Hech qanday biznes logika yo'q.

---

## Presenter

Barcha logika shu yerda.

```txt
Validation
API Calls
State
Calculations
```

---

## Model

Data bilan ishlaydi.

---

## Request Lifecycle

```txt
Button Click
 ↓
Presenter
 ↓
Model
 ↓
Presenter
 ↓
View
```

---

## Afzalliklari

* Test qilish juda oson
* View juda sodda

---

## Kamchiliklari

Presenter juda katta bo'lib ketadi.

---

# 6. MVVM (Model View ViewModel)

Bugungi frontendning asosiy patternlaridan biri.

---

## Strukturasi

```txt
View
 ↕
ViewModel
 ↕
Model
```

---

## View

UI.

React JSX.

Vue Template.

Angular Template.

---

## ViewModel

State va UI logikasi.

Masalan:

```txt
useUsers()
useAuth()
useProducts()
```

---

## Model

API va data.

---

## React misoli

```txt
View
↓
Component

ViewModel
↓
Custom Hook

Model
↓
API Service
```

---

## Real loyiha

```txt
Profile Page
 ↓
useProfile()
 ↓
UserService
 ↓
API
```

---

## Afzalliklari

* React uchun ideal
* Test qilish oson
* UI va Business Logic ajraladi

---

## Kamchiliklari

* Dastlab tushunish qiyin

---

# 7. Layered Architecture

Enterprise loyihalarda eng ko'p ishlatiladigan pattern.

---

## Strukturasi

```txt
Presentation Layer
↓
Application Layer
↓
Business Layer
↓
Data Access Layer
↓
Database
```

---

## Presentation Layer

UI.

Misollar:

```txt
React
Vue
Angular
```

---

## Application Layer

Use Cases.

Masalan:

```txt
Login
Create User
Delete User
```

---

## Business Layer

Asosiy qoidalar.

Masalan:

```txt
18 yoshdan kichik foydalanuvchi
kredit ololmaydi
```

---

## Data Access Layer

Database bilan ishlaydi.

```txt
Repository
ORM
Query Builder
```

---

## Afzalliklari

* Katta enterprise loyihalar uchun qulay
* Test yozish oson

---

## Kamchiliklari

* Kichik loyihalar uchun ortiqcha

---

# 8. Clean Architecture

Robert C. Martin (Uncle Bob) tomonidan yaratilgan.

Eng muhim arxitekturalardan biri.

---

## Strukturasi

```txt
Presentation
↓
Application
↓
Domain
↓
Infrastructure
```

---

## Domain

Eng markaziy qism.

Bu yerda:

```txt
Entities
Business Rules
```

joylashadi.

---

## Application

Use Cases.

Masalan:

```txt
Create User
Approve Order
```

---

## Infrastructure

Tashqi tizimlar.

```txt
Database
Redis
RabbitMQ
Email
```

---

## Presentation

Frontend yoki API.

---

## Dependency Rule

Faqat ichkariga bog'lanish mumkin.

```txt
Presentation
 ↓
Application
 ↓
Domain
```

Teskari bog'lanish mumkin emas.

